    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride that's built to last! This vehicle is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it, making it a fantastic value for anyone looking for dependable transportation. While it shows some honest signs of its journey with visible wear and tear both inside and out, it remains a solid choice that gets the job done. Don't miss out on this practical and budget-friendly option!",
